{
  "stem": "25651.12",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, to them, it must have been bizarre.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was bizarre.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And many of the Hungarian Jews were in caftans, you know, sort of-- they were already camped out there for days waiting, really literally waiting to be gassed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So a few young men take me to a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He questions me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he asks, Yiddish, you see-- he asks why are you talking Yiddish like, like German, [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] Yiddish is [NON-ENGLISH], you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why is your Yiddish like German?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, look, I come from Moravia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I learned Yiddish from Jewish people who came from yeshivot in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's the Yiddish I know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So he says to the people around him, this is a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This is a, a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, he's trying to tell us something to do, which will cost us our lives.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he's a German boy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He's not a Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the topsy-turvy world of Auschwitz, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I go on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I talk to some more people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, they don't believe you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] If I tell you, you're going to walk out of here, and the car is going to come and knock you down, and you're going to die, you know, outside the front door, you'll never believe me.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the same in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It doesn't matter how much you tell them, they won't believe you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it is actually an unbelievable story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I often think today, you know, is this the reality?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or was that the reality?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it's so unreal to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, next morning there's an explosion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And within 20 minutes, the Germans have got it under control.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
